{"tid":1961313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日最後一日反對長者優先投訴/限制點票人數","createTime":"2020-04-06T16:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T17:27:16.000Z","uid":223741,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f12738ff37939ea45157b4707db65d1745e28f43","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:50:14.000Z","msg":"2019年區議會選舉投票人數創新高，大批選民到票站投票，引致大排長龍。選舉管理委員會今日發布2020立法會選舉活動指引諮詢文件，主席<span style=\"color: red;\">馮驊建議票站主任可以作出安排方便有特別需要的選民，例如年滿70歲的長者、孕婦和傷殘人士投票可考慮優先投票</span>。另外，<span style=\"color: red;\">選管會亦考慮實名記錄進入票站人士及限制觀看點票人數</span>，並考慮派選舉事務處人員拍攝點票情況。諮詢4月7日截止。"},{"pid":"74d487876142137f835e04b522eef8ae0d3398ad","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:50:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/27686/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E9%81%B8%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%83-%E9%A6%AE%E9%A9%8A-27689/%E3%80%90%E4%B9%9D%E6%9C%88%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E3%80%91%E9%81%B8%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%83%E6%93%AC%E6%94%B9%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95-70%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AF%E5%84%AA%E5%85%88%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F27686%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E9%25A9%258A-27689%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%2594%25B9%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25BC%2595-70%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%2585%2588%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le%2FzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=85a9285b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/27686/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E9%81%B8%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%83-%E9%A6%AE%E9%A9%8A-27689/%E3%80%90%E4%B9%9D%E6%9C%88%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E3%80%91%E9%81%B8%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%83%E6%93%AC%E6%94%B9%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95-70%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AF%E5%84%AA%E5%85%88%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8</a>"},{"pid":"828dbb286fb70fa72532479e05746362ae37df1c","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"eacenq@eac.hk<br />\n<br />\n<ins>反對年滿70歲人士可優先投票及限制點票站觀票人數</ins><br />\n<br />\n致選舉委員會：<br />\n<br />\n我就選管會就新一屆立法會換屆選舉的選舉活動指引提出反對，反對限制觀看點票人數，以及年滿70歲可優先投票。<br />\n<br />\n首先，根據過往選舉經驗而言，大部份長者選民一般選擇在早上投票。假若長者選民擁有優先投票權，其他需要在早上投票後上班的市民便會增加其時間成本，造成不公平。然而，選舉管理委員會(選管會)應當呼籲長者選民可於其他時段進行投票，避免在票站開站或關閉前的高峰時段前往投票。<br />\n<br />\n再者，即使在過去選舉當中出現長龍，投票過程都十分順利，並無出現大量長者投訴或出現身體不適，可見他們為了投下神聖一票也不會拒絕排隊。若然要解決排長龍這個問題，本人建議可以加開票站疏導，而非使用優先投票這種治標不治本的方法。即使長者能優先投票，人龍依舊存在，並會分開了兩條人龍，更容易造成混亂。<br />\n<br />\n本人建議選管會可以根據2019年區議會選舉時的平等原則作出靈活安排，在排隊人數眾多的時候向未能長時間站立的選民坐下等候，並記下他們的輪候位置，以便在輪到他們的輪候位置時安排他們到發票櫃枱領取選票。<br />\n<br />\n抗議現行法例阻礙18歲人士做選民<br />\n<br />\n本人亦不滿現時法例阻撓部份在選舉日已年滿18歲的人登記成為選民。現時在非區議會選舉年，一名永久性居民要在申請登記為選民後的首個七月二十五日(若為區議會選舉年則為九月二十五日)年滿18歲才成為合資格選民。換言之如果他在2020年7月26日才滿18歲，將無法在2020年度做選民。<br />\n<br />\n反觀外國的做法及法例就不同。加拿大和澳門的做法類似，未滿18歲的人可以事先登記，一到18歲，他們的選民身份就會轉為正式登記，並可以行使選民的權利。<br />\n<br />\n香港的做法是純粹因行政方便而無理剝奪他人選民資格，恐遭司法覆核，選管會應立即修正！<br />\n<br />\n另外本人反對限制觀看點票人數。這會令一些打算觀看點票，以監察選舉結果公平公正的人士無法進入點票站。<br />\n<br />\n本人希望選管會能夠三思而行，盡力在選舉工作上做到公平公正，避免畫蛇添足，招人懷疑。<br />\n<br />\n香港市民"},{"pid":"9bb5195ca853dcef91618473a28696aa222c21d3","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:03:38.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"4a1ce1d9b3603d11d71a154e6159ecfc2a785053","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"a088b053a97c031d8273d747ac82e279097e2064","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:04:04.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"2590da04f7dc7292ec42502d28b954ea13c8ad67","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:04:28.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"7c20e61918e46f13ace1352e5e09902fd7903c90","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:05:13.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"b7293dc40d006cdd6d87d5008490e56a2fb0aa95","tid":1961313,"uid":247894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:05:56.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"d2c651cb4f57cfd856f90a5355a975b8d143c43c","tid":1961313,"uid":50891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:07:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68c97e9ba190f9a61b58ed970978350d36f460c3","tid":1961313,"uid":17055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:08:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23ef759587bd21873ce10e260f3bd621a71cdd05","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:08:53.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"684608d90aaf00c5b70757db23d0c03a8bc813f7","tid":1961313,"uid":228040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:09:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4546c837b3c982d4871c9a43cb33c85353693f","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:10:12.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"b642ef4b80164b4da172b062539d8ff6726f10eb","tid":1961313,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:10:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26db1e2e1c309694e33bd50cd8027233264dd0b8","tid":1961313,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:11:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd00a697c7d591fa8ec1a413382d3e33ad2897cb","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:12:37.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"c935b803d7b0865b739fb72f900938908ed28575","tid":1961313,"uid":289782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:12:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b30a309420eb82dc536af59955bfaac0e004bc7","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:13:03.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"fa9891a891405fd9dcfaf39814bef382bfecf851","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:13:32.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"31b33a878e3f83bdbfba3250d54bfac0902b77ce","tid":1961313,"uid":73948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:16:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"754f213b7fdd6445f1eb2606de48bc2512d92b6c","tid":1961313,"uid":47978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b3df444caee3a11bd49670968a3f0836269112","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e758ff776b9a8c39825f34769566e941d3b10566","tid":1961313,"uid":273682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"828dbb286fb70fa72532479e05746362ae37df1c","tid":1961313,"uid":223741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":